{"type": "article", "id": 23377, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 24473, "name": "hollis+ morris"}, {"id": 24474, "name": "Vanmoof"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 23627, "name": "Pop & Pac"}, {"id": 15672, "name": "Marcel Wanders"}, {"id": 24475, "name": "Julius Bučelis"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154029qaQL3rhRvNFZcV91.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>hollis+ morris product</h2>\n<p>这是多伦多的设计工作室 hollis+morris 推出的家具系列，以木质家具为主。他们追求极简而抽象的审美，比如挂在墙上的灯就像一道闪电，而边桌则有近似三角形的支撑结构，让桌子有了相应的朝向。而看似简单的椅子也有细小的转折结构，都流露出一种简单的优雅。<a href=\"http://www.hollismorris.com\">这里是网站主页。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160135ckqW42zNmJFge3Hs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160135ZbvV0Y16jqLWdT3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160135t2GfPC4IjXphkJ6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160137XtUyTeV1javrdnMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160137MxIu9p6Bc4CJtUf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mad Collection by Poliform &amp; Marcel Wanders</h2>\n<p>这是荷兰设计师 Marcel Wanders 为他的 Mad 系列增加的家具，包括双人沙发、扶手椅等。双人沙发只有半边靠背，是不对称的，从而强调了后面流畅优雅的曲线。而带圆桌面的扶手椅 Mad King 与此同理，因圆桌面打破了对称，让人注意到有曲线的轮廓。另一款 Mad Queen 椅子外形更圆，用菱形网格让椅子表现出装饰感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160138G68qrHFw7sKNPSYB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160138meFB3V8oaGI0yNzL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601390tHLBQwaJzkxDWih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160140cjFWOBiZN7ekosQH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160141ERgNLbABWks7OZV0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BONCHO by Vanmoof</h2>\n<p>这是荷兰自行车品牌 VANMOOF 专为城市骑行者设计的折叠式雨衣，拉开拉链后就直接弹出一件雨衣，从头覆盖到手，弧度可以引导雨水滑落。它的圆框结构刚好在手的位置，有一定的固定作用，可以防止滑落。将它缩小成圆形的小包后能直接挂在自行车车杆下，很方便。可以选择蓝、灰、黄三种颜色和三种型号，<a href=\"http://vanmoof.com/boncho/156-boncho-mint.html\">这里是预定链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160141E3yxFSnlM2Zwjzar.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64095238\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060616014247qo6snGlfbrOmea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.25047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160142vfPCklDbAMU8FcOV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160143vuO6yWzh0EnjxI5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160143kvU3lza0mBtwu7JI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Grid 03 by Nendo</h2>\n<p>这是 Nendo 为致敬绘图人员系列手表推出的新款，之前两款 01 Scale 和 02 Stencil 的分别取材于直尺和手绘工具尺，表盘内的刻度与尺子的刻度相对应。而这一款则取材于三角板，表盘内有三角板上的方形网格，另有数字刻度和两圈秒表刻度，是刻度最明确的一款手表。表盘直径 36 毫米，用不锈钢制作，有棕色、海军蓝和灰色三种，都配有相应颜色的皮质表带。售价 145.83 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/all/draftsman-03-grid/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160144oe2MtSTfvwykiqsH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160144DjVb2F64lgJxvpuI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601450RZNaGT5YvmewMj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83012821\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160145fob7jDyQPgxqiOMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601468GZIHX6mlEnYuq53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601468KfqhUQEAblHD2mj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>DROP by Julius Bučelis</h2>\n<p>手机、平板和电脑的屏幕都需要清洗维护，但想必很少有人会使用专用的清洁剂和抹布这样的搭配吧。立陶宛设计师 Julius Bučelis 就将它们合二为一设计了这个小工具，正方形的布料里装上清洁液体，相当于瓶身，其中一个角削掉安装了喷雾头，在喷洒液体之后就可以马上擦拭了。扁平的“瓶身”相较于圆形瓶身也更容易装在包里。这个设计获得了 2015 年 IF 奖，<a href=\"http://bucelis.com/#drop\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160147ICBUwkuMxoREHsiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601479uXIkVRLolmDehZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160148GSx5m23J9aOvib4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160148vURz0dXyElYOqPax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061601488CLd1phFw7DbqE5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Square One Coffee Roasters package by Pop &amp; Pac</h2>\n<p>这组咖啡包装来自澳大利亚平面设计工作室 Pop &amp; Pac，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/22490.html\">不久前我们介绍了他们设计的墨尔本高人气的咖啡馆 Operator 25 。</a>三个圆筒形的咖啡罐上都有着令人晕眩的图案，像是一圈一圈处于流动状态的波纹，非常魔幻。设计方并不想用咖啡的图案或者任何文字，仅仅以这些波纹让它们独特而有辨识度。其中红色是浓缩咖啡，蓝色是普通咖啡，绿色是速溶咖啡。<a href=\"http://www.pop-pac.com/#/project/square-one\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160149wO8HsnEJV7loa3AT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160149vnKU1tbwcZqk3a9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160150JqGmY97CrIkfXwzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160150YVF1vCQdymcAMIug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160151ZGIlCfWibXrKstkz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}